{{Quote|We replaced your missing escape pods. Upgraded the tractor beam generator to a Mark Seven, and the hyperdrive motivator to a Series Four-oh-one—''"<br />"''Holy mother of meteors.|A New Republic yard boss and Han Solo|<ref name="Before the Storm">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref>}}
The '''Series 401 [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] [[Hyperdrive motivator/Legends|motivator]]''' was the primary [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] propulsion system of the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] following its upgrade from a [[Isu-Sim/Legends|Isu-Sim]] [[SSP05 hyperdrive generator/Legends|SSP05 hyperdrive generator]].

This was considered to be a "more efficient" unit, but apparently had the same Hyperdrive Rating of 0.5 as the heavily-modified SSP05 (though it is technically possible that the drives were merely swapped back to restore the Falcon's previous 0.5 rating by the end of the [[Black Fleet Crisis]]).<ref name="Cracken's Threat Dossier">''[[Cracken's Threat Dossier]]''</ref>

